@node Description "Description"

Description
-----------

Icon is a Custom Class of the Magic User Interface © by Stefan Stuntz.	It's a subclass of area-class.

@{"MUI" link MUIReadMe} public custom class which allows use of an icon's render and select images for display in a gadget.  Depending on the gadget's select state the appropriate image will be displayed.
@endnode

